Abuhachi: OH, HEY. YOUR PARTNER
CAME BY FOR A VISIT LAST NIGHT.

00:22:13.946 --> 00:22:18.980
HE SAID TO GIVE YOU THIS
IF YOU HAPPENED TO SHOW UP.

00:22:18.980 --> 00:22:22.080
SO THEN, LET ME ASK YOU THIS.

00:22:22.080 --> 00:22:24.446
WHO SHOULD I BET ON TONIGHT?

